{"tid":684111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★原本1971年，已經預留紅磡火車站3-6號月台地底會起地鐵站","createTime":"2018-05-30T09:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T09:08:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8fe036d4a80d4e02ba6ea18326f012ead43e7199","tid":684111,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/12/142037_48f7f9f2f2802ebfaa848450c6acdfa8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F12%2F142037_48f7f9f2f2802ebfaa848450c6acdfa8.png&h=dd67781f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAccess to the podium was obtained by means of flyovers and bridges serving the ferry and surrounding residential areas. The station was designed to accommodate the future MTR East Kowloon Line and provision was made for an escalator link to the proposed underground station.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://industrialhistoryhk.org/kowloon-canton-railway-british-section-kowloon-station-relocation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Findustrialhistoryhk.org%2Fkowloon-canton-railway-british-section-kowloon-station-relocation%2F&d=PTTdPivMZrlUXxKst%2FMdAcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c1ab9596\" target=\"_blank\">http://industrialhistoryhk.org/kowloon-canton-railway-british-section-kowloon-station-relocation/</a>"},{"pid":"926d08d55ad3daeb228b35158365c15a4704e1f1","tid":684111,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"即係現在紅磡火車站地底有預留空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}